on\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wjh1665702607394.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wjh1665702607394.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wjh1665702607394.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wjh1665702607394\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Message Line </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The  MessageLine property determines whether\n      the message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window. This is used to display\n      non-obtrusive messages to the user. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__topic_d97628e1_d97629e1_d97630e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__p_d97631e1_d97632e1_d97633e1\">\n             MessageLine <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Default</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__section_w1154ab1b5b3_w1155ab1b5_w1156ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__p_d97634e1_d97635e1_d97636e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\" \"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__section_w1157ab1b5b5_w1158ab1b5_w1159ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Default</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Undefined. Use the default as defined in <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>. </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11024e1_d11025e1_d11026e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No message line is displayed.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__section_fjp_yvl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d324010e173\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__table_d11027e1_d11028e1_d11029e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__section_zfw_zvl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d324010e222\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__p_d97643e1_d97644e1_d97645e1\">The message line is used to display runtime messages\n            to the user. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">message</span> statement sends\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageText</var> to the message line, so if you choose to hide the\n            message line, you should ensure that it is made visible before sending a message to the\n            message line, or provide an alternative way of communicating with the user (for example,\n            using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">askmess</span>).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__section_hcj_2wl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d324010e241\">Example: Setting in usys.ini</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__pre_q2x_kxl_4wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\nshell=ushell(MessageLine=false)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__section_wcb_lxl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d324010e250\">Example: Setting in ProcScript </h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__pre_nrp_nxl_4wb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$applproperties()=\"MessageLine=false\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__section_ect_nxl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d324010e259\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wjh1665702607394__p_d97655e1_d97656e1_d97657e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ohj1705472401504.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ohj1705472401504.html\" title=\"An application shell is a module used to initialize and run an application (Windows or character-based) or application server.\">Application Shells</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ubi1665702607312.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>message</a><p>Display the specified string in the message line (if it is available), or an interactive dialog box.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifq1665702843454.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$applproperties</a><p>Set the presentation properties of the application shell.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gma1665702671256.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Shell</a><p>Sets the default window properties of the application shell.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616731\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616731\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Message Line Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Message Line The MessageLine property determines whether the message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window. This is used to display non-obtrusive messages to the user. MessageLine = Default | True | False Example: \" \" Value Description Default Undefined. Use the default as defined in usys.ini . True Message line is displayed at the bottom of the application window. False No message line is displayed. Usage Dynamic? Yes Dependencies: None Description The message line is used to display runtime messages to the user. The message statement sends MessageText to the message line, so if you choose to hide the message line, you should ensure that it is made visible before sending a message to the message line, or provide an alternative way of communicating with the user (for example, using askmess ). Example: Setting in usys.ini [application] shell=ushell(MessageLine=false) Copy Example: Setting in ProcScript $applproperties()=\"MessageLine=false\" Copy Applies To Application Shells Related Links message Display the specified string in the message line (if it is available), or an interactive dialog box. $applproperties Set the presentation properties of the application shell. Shell Sets the default window properties of the application shell. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}